snippet.title: SPEED DREAMS - FMC GT4 at Alicante
snippet.description:
We have just launched a new Development Post ( https://www.speed-dreams.net/en/development-news-2022-04/ ), and to join it and show you some of the latest work we have been doing lately we have recorded this video. 
In it you can check, for example, the new FX sounds in the game menus (thanks @franzopow), the new Delta HUD widget (Madbad), and also the new interior of the FMC GT4 (thanks @chad3006), which as you know is based/inspired on the 2005 Ford GT. The track this time is Alicante. We hope you enjoy it.

You can find this game and more info about this Open Source project on:
https://www.speed-dreams.net 

#OpenSource #SpeedDreams #SimRacing #Supercars #Alicante
